Access copies of the collection are available through the Folklife Reading Room of the American Folklife Center. Duplication of collection materials may be governed by copyright and other restrictions. Please refer to the AFC web site for information on ordering copies of unpublished recordings (
http://www.loc.gov/folklife/recordering.html
). For specific questions, researchers should consult with the American Folklife Center reference staff.
